						               													<description>This is a Micro-game with 18 cards some cubes and some dices!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game each player control their pack of robotic miners and send them to planet to work and back with resources ( The Victory Points ).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game is a simple and eficient Area Control, Action Select and Dice Selection in a small package.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round consists of two phases. The first is to roll and select, the first in turn rolls the dice and select 3 of them for you and passes the rest to the next player. In the second phase the players used the dice selected to prepare actions in the mother ship and / or send your miners to planets paying the landing value so that the miner can land on the planet that will mining until there is the scoring event that calls the miners back to the player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#10;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#10;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;&amp;#9;Game Components&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     18 Cards&amp;#10;     13 six-faced dices&amp;#10;     24 cubes ( 6 of each color )&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
